```py
import numpy as np
import cupy as cp
import time
```

```py
### Running at CPU using Numpy
start_time = time.time()
myvar_cpu = np.ones((800,800,800))
end_time = time.time()
print(end_time - start_time)

### Running at GPU using CuPy
start_time = time.time()
myvar_gpu = cp.ones((800,800,800))
cp.cuda.Stream.null.synchronize()
end_time = time.time()
print(end_time - start_time)
```
